  "reviewer_considerations": [
    "The Android project does not expose a detekt task; `cd android && ./gradlew detekt` fails with `Task 'detekt' not found`, so the bounded Android gates for this task are unit tests, full Gradle tests, assembleDebug, and sandbox launch.",
    "ThemeAvatar accepts `imageUrl` for parity with the Android component map, but there is no image-loading dependency in this module yet, so sandbox coverage uses deterministic initials and badge states instead of network-backed image fixtures.",
    "UI-009 keeps the new surfaces under `ui/atoms/**` per the sprint task guardrails even though the older component map classifies `Collapsible` and `FAB` higher in the stack."
  ],
